{"hash":"ec5e50c96b423917fd23f8317f4a3bf99d08681d","data":{"post":{"title":"Goreme","author":"","date":"2022-09-30","content":"<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20220930_072447.jpg\"></p>\n<p>We starten in de lounge van Rotterdam Airport.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20220930_175421.jpg\"></p>\n<p>Uitzicht vanuit ons hotel, dat is nog wat anders dan het platte landschap in Nederland. We verbleven in de Elite Cave Suites. Echte aanrader, op het ontbijt na dan.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20220930_180326.jpg\"></p>\n<p>Zonsondergang op de berg boven ons hotel.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221001_070254.jpg\"></p>\n<p>Sta je op en zie je ineens allemaal dit om je heen!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221001_063521.jpg\"></p>\n<p>Bizar!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221001_101231.jpg\"></p>\n<p>Rest van de dag zijn we rond gaan touren. Verschillende plekken bezocht en genieten van het uitzicht.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221001_112654.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221001_110237.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221001_140037.jpg\"></p>\n<p>We dalen af naar de Ilhara Vallei.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221001_140843.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221001_142047.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221001_142319.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221001_143657.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221001_161901.jpg\"></p>\n<p>Op naar de Selime Kathedraal.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221001_162943.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221001_163952.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221001_194332.jpg\"></p>\n<p>Tijd voor avondeten!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221002_060419.jpg\"></p>\n<p>In de vroege ochtend de berg opgegaan om de luchtbalonnen als eerste te zien opstijgen.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221002_061835.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221002_063435.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221002_063816.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221002_064819.jpg\"></p>\n<p>Met zonsopgang!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221002_070713.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221003_102819.jpg\"></p>\n<p>En weer rond touren.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221003_111035.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221003_114856.jpg\"></p>\n","id":"0d90d76e9aeea8e459ab084f0929dc87","path":"/blog/turkije-2022/goreme/","image":"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20220930_175421.jpg","category":{"title":"Goreme, Antalya, Istanbul - Turkije","id":"Goreme, Antalya, Istanbul - Turkije","belongsTo":{"edges":[{"node":{"title":"Goreme","path":"/blog/turkije-2022/goreme/","id":"0d90d76e9aeea8e459ab084f0929dc87","excerpt":"Goreme ook wel bekend voor de 'Insta' luchtbalonnen en mooie landschappen."}},{"node":{"title":"Antalya","path":"/blog/turkije-2022/antalya/","id":"2ece3ea708db0595e414f89dc2859cef","excerpt":"Lekker toerist spelen en genieten van het lekkere weer."}},{"node":{"title":"Istanbul","path":"/blog/turkije-2022/istanbul/","id":"a62793c520acf35e2cfc127c29f10371","excerpt":"Istanbul. Druk."}}]}}}},"context":{}}